<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Foodie Express</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Outfit:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Custom Styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/About.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar.ejs') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="about-hero position-relative d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-center pt-5">
        <div class="overlay position-absolute w-100 h-100"></div>
        <div class="container position-relative z-index-1 text-white">
            <span class="badge bg-danger mb-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-pill shadow-sm">About Us</span>
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4 font-outfit">Savor the Moment with <br><span class="text-warning">Foodie Express</span></h1>
            <p class="lead mx-auto" style="max-width: 700px; font-weight: 300;">
                Foodie Express is a fast and reliable food delivery platform created with passion and dedication. Our mission is to connect hungry customers with their favorite restaurants in the fastest, easiest way possible.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container my-5">
      <!-- Story Section -->
      <div class="row align-items-center my-5 py-lg-5">
          <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0 pe-lg-5">
              <div class="position-relative ps-4 pt-4">
                  <!-- Decorative background block -->
                  <div class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-75 h-75 bg-danger rounded-4 opacity-10"></div>
                  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504674900247-0877df9cc836?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow-lg position-relative" alt="Delicious Food">
                  <div class="experience-badge position-absolute bg-white rounded-4 shadow-lg p-3 text-center border-bottom border-danger border-4">
                      <h2 class="text-danger fw-bold mb-0 font-outfit">2+</h2>
                      <p class="text-muted mb-0 small fw-bold text-uppercase">Years of<br>Excellence</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
              <h6 class="text-danger text-uppercase fw-bold letter-spacing-1 mb-2">Our Mission</h6>
              <h2 class="fw-bold font-outfit mb-4 display-6">Delivering Happiness, <br>One Meal at a Time.</h2>
              <p class="text-muted mb-4 fs-5" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                  Whether it's breakfast, lunch, dinner, or a late-night snack — we’re here to deliver. We carefully curate our restaurant partners to ensure you get the highest quality food, piping hot, right to your doorstep.
              </p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0 feature-list">
                  <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-center p-3 bg-white rounded-3 shadow-sm border-start border-danger border-4"><i class="fas fa-motorcycle text-danger me-3 fs-4"></i> <span class="fw-semibold">Fast & Reliable Delivery under 30 mins</span></li>
                  <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-center p-3 bg-white rounded-3 shadow-sm border-start border-warning border-4"><i class="fas fa-store text-warning me-3 fs-4"></i> <span class="fw-semibold">100+ Local Premium Restaurant Partners</span></li>
                  <li class="d-flex align-items-center p-3 bg-white rounded-3 shadow-sm border-start border-success border-4"><i class="fas fa-headset text-success me-3 fs-4"></i> <span class="fw-semibold">24/7 Dedicated Customer Support</span></li>
              </ul>
          </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Team Section -->
      <div class="team-section text-center py-5 px-3 rounded-5 mb-5 shadow-sm mt-5">
          <h6 class="text-danger text-uppercase fw-bold letter-spacing-1 mb-2">Our People</h6>
          <h2 class="fw-bold font-outfit mb-5 display-6">Meet The Creators</h2>
          
          <div class="row justify-content-center g-4 px-lg-4">
              <!-- Member 1 -->
              <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
                  <div class="team-card text-center bg-white p-3 rounded-4 shadow-sm h-100">
                      <div class="img-wrapper mb-3 mx-auto">
                          <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/e8/86/27/e8862709fd7193e2c20930554a627e15.jpg" class="rounded-circle shadow-sm" alt="Nguyễn Duy Rim" />
                      </div>
                      <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Nguyễn Duy Rim</h6>
                      <p class="text-danger small mb-0 fw-semibold">Leader</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Member 2 -->
              <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
                  <div class="team-card text-center bg-white p-3 rounded-4 shadow-sm h-100">
                      <div class="img-wrapper mb-3 mx-auto">
                          <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/5b/e7/d4/5be7d474f77c7ecf26d50072049e435c.jpg" class="rounded-circle shadow-sm" alt="Trần Nguyễn Hoàng Phúc" />
                      </div>
                      <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">T. N. Hoàng Phúc</h6>
                      <p class="text-danger small mb-0 fw-semibold">Developer</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Member 3 -->
              <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
                  <div class="team-card text-center bg-white p-3 rounded-4 shadow-sm h-100">
                      <div class="img-wrapper mb-3 mx-auto">
                          <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/5f/78/fa/5f78faf0649bab7f7f2afd0fe284ced8.jpg" class="rounded-circle shadow-sm" alt="Lê Quang Bách" />
                      </div>
                      <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Lê Quang Bách</h6>
                      <p class="text-danger small mb-0 fw-semibold">Developer</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Member 4 -->
              <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
                  <div class="team-card text-center bg-white p-3 rounded-4 shadow-sm h-100">
                      <div class="img-wrapper mb-3 mx-auto">
                          <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/15/82/6c/15826c8fca27e18276bd2f0b25cbbc3c.jpg" class="rounded-circle shadow-sm" alt="Nguyễn Thanh Tùng" />
                      </div>
                      <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">N. Thanh Tùng</h6>
                      <p class="text-danger small mb-0 fw-semibold">Designer</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Member 5 -->
              <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
                  <div class="team-card text-center bg-white p-3 rounded-4 shadow-sm h-100">
                      <div class="img-wrapper mb-3 mx-auto">
                          <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/af/f4/56/aff45698092ec2541d641407584d5fc0.jpg" class="rounded-circle shadow-sm" alt="Nguyễn Quang Tâm" />
                      </div>
                      <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">N. Quang Tâm</h6>
                      <p class="text-danger small mb-0 fw-semibold">Marketing</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline Section -->
      <div class="timeline-section py-5 mb-4">
          <div class="text-center mb-5">
              <h6 class="text-danger text-uppercase fw-bold letter-spacing-1 mb-2">Our Journey</h6>
              <h2 class="fw-bold font-outfit display-6">Development Timeline</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="timeline-modern position-relative mx-auto mt-5" style="max-width: 800px;">
              <!-- 2023 -->
              <div class="timeline-item-modern d-flex mb-4">
                  <div class="timeline-year text-end pe-4 w-25">
                      <h3 class="fw-bold text-danger mb-0 font-outfit">2023</h3>
                  </div>
                  <div class="timeline-marker position-relative">
                      <div class="marker-dot bg-danger border border-4 border-white rounded-circle shadow"></div>
                      <div class="marker-line bg-light position-absolute h-100 start-50 translate-middle-x"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="timeline-content ps-4 w-75 pb-4">
                      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 bg-white">
                          <div class="card-body p-4">
                              <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">Idea Generation</h5>
                              <p class="text-muted mb-0">Ý tưởng được hình thành với tầm nhìn tạo ra một nền tảng giao đồ ăn nhanh chóng và tiện lợi cho mọi người.</p>
                          </div>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- 2024 -->
              <div class="timeline-item-modern d-flex mb-4">
                  <div class="timeline-year text-end pe-4 w-25">
                      <h3 class="fw-bold text-danger mb-0 font-outfit">2024</h3>
                  </div>
                  <div class="timeline-marker position-relative">
                      <div class="marker-dot bg-danger border border-4 border-white rounded-circle shadow"></div>
                      <div class="marker-line bg-light position-absolute h-100 start-50 translate-middle-x"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="timeline-content ps-4 w-75 pb-4">
                      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 bg-white">
                          <div class="card-body p-4">
                              <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">Development Begins</h5>
                              <p class="text-muted mb-0">Bắt đầu phát triển ứng dụng với nhóm nhỏ, xây dựng tính năng đặt món, theo dõi đơn hàng và đánh giá cửa hàng trực tuyến.</p>
                          </div>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- 2025 -->
              <div class="timeline-item-modern d-flex">
                  <div class="timeline-year text-end pe-4 w-25">
                      <h3 class="fw-bold text-danger mb-0 font-outfit">2025</h3>
                  </div>
                  <div class="timeline-marker position-relative">
                      <div class="marker-dot bg-danger border border-4 border-white rounded-circle shadow"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="timeline-content ps-4 w-75">
                      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 bg-white border-bottom border-danger border-4">
                          <div class="card-body p-4">
                              <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">Official Launch</h5>
                              <p class="text-muted mb-0">Ra mắt phiên bản chính thức, hợp tác với hơn 100 nhà hàng địa phương và mở rộng thị trường ra toàn quốc.</p>
                          </div>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer.ejs') %>
